          <!-- Program options -->
           <h3 class="w_a_headding"><strong>Program Options</strong></h3>
           
           <p>Wolverine Access offers flexible program options for students to choose from. In Canvas, on the Textbooks & Course Materials page, you'll be able to change your program choice as much as you want and enjoy complimentary access to all digital books up until the <a href="https://store.uvu.edu/wolverine-access-important-dates" style="color:#0e8345;">opt out deadline</a> each semester.</p>
           
           <p>Some instructors use free resources such as <a href="https://www.uvu.edu/otl/instructional_design/oer.html" target="_blank" style="color:#0e8345;">Open Educational Resources</a> (OER) for their courses. Free resources can help offset the cost of paid materials and keep the overall flat rate amount low. Free materials, such as OER, will always be accessible to you regardless of which program option you choose.</p>
           
